values: I met a girl today. She thought I was hideous. I started to cry... and ... well ... seeing as my tears are brown.... she ran away screaming. It made me cry more....in fact I'm still crying. *POOOOT* Sorry, had to blow my nose.  But she was a cute girl... BOOHOOHOO*PFFFFTT*

My cat jumped and scared me. It made me cry.  Let me tell you, when I cry, it is sad.... Because I only have one eye... and that eye is already puckered... OH GOD... The memory is making me cry!! OH WHY!!!! OOHOOHHHOHOHH*POOT*

I don't get it. People seem to hate me so much. I guess it's because I'm such a loner and I don't talk to people. WHY MUST EVERYONE HAT ME? Sometimes I wish I could just kill myself... I just end up crying and crying until I pass out... the only problem is, well... I have a disfigurement where my face is actually an ass.. so when I cry... it's like... liquid... erm... and sometimes, when I really cry hard... a little.. erm... nugget comes out... it really drives people away, which makes me cry even more, so its a vicious cycle.... BOOOHOOOHOOOO*PHHHHHHHHHHHHTTT*.... ewwwwwww.
I think I am so depressed because, well...grandma molests my cat right in front of me then slaps me on the ass.
